NAME
    Lingua::Multinational::Translit::ICAO -- Multinational characters
    transliteration into ICAO Doc 9303

SYNOPSIS
     use Lingua::Multinational::Translit::ICAO qw/ ml2icao /;

     print ml2icao('word', 'iso-8859-1');

DESCRIPTION
    Lingua::Multinational::Translit::ICAO can be used for transliteration of
    multinational characters in conformance with ICAO Doc 9303
    Recommendations.

METHODS
  ml2icao ( $string, [ $encoding ])
    This method converts $string from multinational character set to ICAO
    transliteration.

    Optional $encoding parameter allows to specify $string's encoding
    (default is 'utf-8')

